name: Timber Time
description:
I always wanted to make a infinite runner - and here it is. Well, a small prototype of one. 

I hope you can enjoy this little piece of software without sound and with only a little bit of content - I did not have the time to finish it (family dad, fulltime employe and gamedev at night).

But there still is a game to play for the KenneyJam - so: have fun!
